   July 4: Talk-show host Geraldo Rivera is 57. Musician Domingo
Ortiz of Widespread Panic is 48. Singer John Waite is 45. Musician
Kirk Pengilly of INXS is 42. Musician Matt Malley of Counting Crows
is 37. Actress Jenica Bergere (''The Drew Carey Show'') is 26.
Singer Stephen ''Ste'' McNally of BMak is 22.
</P>
