   July 5: Singer Huey Lewis is 50. Musician Bengt Lagerberg of the
Cardigans is 27.
</P>
<P>
   July 6: Actress-singer Della Reese is 69. Actor Ned Beatty is
63. Actor Sylvester Stallone is 54. Actor Geoffrey Rush (''Shine'')
is 49. Actresses Tia and Tamera Mowry (''Sister, Sister'') are 22.
