morning it felt better,'' said Alomar, who was in the lineup
Wednesday night.
</P>
<P>
   Lofton is expected to return Friday or Saturday.
</P>
<P>
   ''They said if it got better today, I could probably play
tomorrow,'' he said. ''That's the way this game goes.''
</P>
