Nasdaq Ends Up 81; Dow Gains 23
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks rose today after the Federal Reserve said it would
leave interest rates unchanged for now. The Dow Jones industrial average rose
23.33 to 10,527.79. Advancing issues outnumbered decliners 1,790-1,112 on the
New York Stock Exchange. The Nasdaq composite index rose 81.38 to 3,940.34.
